def max_ones_after_one_move(s: str) -> int:
    mdif = +1
    cdif = -1
    oone = 0
    for i in range(len(s)):
        if s[i] == '1':
            oone += 1
        val = 1 if s[i] == '0' else -1
        cdif = max(val, cdif + val)
        mdif = max(cdif, mdif)
    return oone + mdif
